"4:4:13" : {s: 4, a: 4, w: 13, r: "هنا", t: "هَنِيٓـًۭٔا", l: "هَنِيٓـٔ", lc: 4, tl: "hanīan", lb: "সুখকর, স্বাস্থ্যকর, তৃপ্তিদায়ক, আরামদায়ক",e: "(in) satisfaction", b: "সানন্দে", f: 4, rm: "to anoint a camel with pitch, be wholesome, make the food, wholesome, easy to digest, do good, promote health. haniun - take it and make use of it, make use of your advantage and profit."},
